334
00:16:53,870 --> 00:16:56,260
with the National Government,

335
00:16:56,280 --> 00:16:57,260
site selection suggestions,

336
00:16:57,280 --> 00:16:59,780
the experience and lessons
from previous cooperation

337
00:16:59,800 --> 00:17:00,450
with the government,

338
00:17:00,950 --> 00:17:02,330
Ma Juncai's rags-to-riches story,

339
00:17:02,680 --> 00:17:05,130
and the political and business resources
of the forces behind him.

340
00:17:06,080 --> 00:17:06,850
It also includes

341
00:17:06,870 --> 00:17:08,740
the shareholder structure
