362
00:18:02,440 --> 00:18:03,660
For confidentiality purposes,

363
00:18:03,680 --> 00:18:05,660
Greater China Pharmaceuticals
is entrusted

364
00:18:06,000 --> 00:18:07,180
to sign the contract with you.

365
00:18:09,790 --> 00:18:11,370
May we have a look

366
00:18:11,520 --> 00:18:14,020
at the entrustment agreement

367
00:18:14,040 --> 00:18:14,850
you signed?

368
00:18:16,310 --> 00:18:18,180
