375
00:18:33,920 --> 00:18:37,020
the products will not be used
in the civil war,

376
00:18:37,520 --> 00:18:39,050
and all proceeds will be donated

377
00:18:39,310 --> 00:18:41,530
to the war effort
resisting Japanese invaders.

378
00:18:42,790 --> 00:18:45,090
