379
00:18:46,000 --> 00:18:46,980
Ms. Chu, relax.

380
00:18:47,240 --> 00:18:49,530
What you just mentioned involves

381
00:18:49,830 --> 00:18:51,570
military, national and partisan issues.

382
00:18:52,310 --> 00:18:54,610
To write them into this contract

383
00:18:55,280 --> 00:18:57,460
may arouse unnecessary disputes.

384
00:18:57,960 --> 00:19:00,740
So we will only make a verbal promise,

385
00:19:01,040 --> 00:19:02,290
instead of putting it in writing.

386
00:19:05,240 --> 00:19:07,370
If that's the case,

387
00:19:08,830 --> 00:19:11,660
I'm afraid we cannot sign

388
00:19:12,240 --> 00:19:13,770
this contract for the time being.

389
00:19:14,070 --> 00:19:14,770
Ms. Chu,

390
00:19:15,720 --> 00:19:16,850
