399
00:19:42,790 --> 00:19:43,460
Mr. Cheng,

400
00:19:44,000 --> 00:19:46,460
may I have a word with Ms. Chu alone?

401
00:19:59,550 --> 00:20:00,290
Ms. Chu,

402
00:20:00,630 --> 00:20:01,260
as long as

403
00:20:02,760 --> 00:20:03,660
you are willing to sign,

404
00:20:03,830 --> 00:20:04,980
we'll give you

405
00:20:06,070 --> 00:20:07,180
50% of shares.

406
00:20:09,590 --> 00:20:11,500
I'm not asking for shares,

407
00:20:12,790 --> 00:20:15,330
but for you to put the commitment
to resist Japan,

408
00:20:15,680 --> 00:20:18,500
into effect in black and white.

409
00:20:18,870 --> 00:20:21,740
Well, I can't agree to this.

410
00:20:22,720 --> 00:20:24,050
Then please have someone

411
00:20:24,390 --> 00:20:26,220
who can agree to my terms

412
00:20:26,350 --> 00:20:27,900
come and negotiate with me.

413
00:20:29,790 --> 00:20:30,700
Ms. Chu,

414
00:20:31,630 --> 00:20:33,130
it is your honor to serve

415
00:20:33,920 --> 00:20:35,290
the people and the country.

416
00:20:35,680 --> 00:20:36,500
Mr. Ma,

417
00:20:36,960 --> 00:20:38,940
to serve the country and the people,

418
00:20:39,200 --> 00:20:41,940
I am willing to donate all my property.

419
00:20:42,480 --> 00:20:45,700
But I fear that some people,

420
00:20:46,150 --> 00:20:47,980
under the banner of patriotism,

421
00:20:48,520 --> 00:20:51,980
sell out our homeland for personal gain.

422
00:20:55,680 --> 00:20:57,420
Well, Ms. Chu,

423
00:20:58,110 --> 00:21:00,570
do you know who the real shareholder

424
00:21:00,960 --> 00:21:02,570
