Came for me?

453
00:23:19,110 --> 00:23:19,740
Yes.

454
00:23:21,550 --> 00:23:22,530
Let's go talk over there.

455
00:23:24,390 --> 00:23:25,370
Just talk right here.

456
00:23:26,960 --> 00:23:29,020
Too many people here. It's noisy.

457
00:23:37,350 --> 00:23:38,460
What would you like to drink?

458
00:23:42,760 --> 00:23:43,570
I know a bit

459
00:23:44,590 --> 00:23:45,740
about your past.

460
00:23:48,760 --> 00:23:50,290
If you want to know more,

461
00:23:50,870 --> 00:23:51,610
feel free to ask me.

462
00:23:52,350 --> 00:23:53,610
I'll tell you everything I know,

463
00:23:53,920 --> 00:23:54,770
without holding anything back.

464
00:23:55,240 --> 00:23:56,980
If my mother were still alive,

465
00:23:57,520 --> 00:23:59,700
she would've never let a woman like you

466
00:23:59,720 --> 00:24:01,260
