If you

488
00:25:16,590 --> 00:25:17,460
leave him,

489
00:25:18,390 --> 00:25:19,940
you'll get 200,000 silver dollars,

490
00:25:20,480 --> 00:25:21,900
plus a foreign-style house.

491
00:25:23,630 --> 00:25:24,660
So rich!

492
00:25:26,310 --> 00:25:26,980
You…

493
00:25:28,790 --> 00:25:30,660
You chose the hard way!

494
00:25:32,550 --> 00:25:33,420
Teach her a lesson!

495
00:25:33,520 --> 00:25:33,980
Hit her!

496
00:25:36,200 --> 00:25:37,370
- Uh!
- You shameless wretch!

497
00:25:37,520 --> 00:25:39,180
How dare you act against Madam!

498
00:25:40,310 --> 00:25:41,700
I must teach you a lesson today,

499
00:25:41,830 --> 00:25:43,900
or you'll never learn the rules!

500
00:25:44,480 --> 00:25:45,050
Meet your end!

501
00:25:45,070 --> 00:25:46,020
Since she's willing to take a beating,

502
00:25:46,310 --> 00:25:47,500
grant her wish!

503
00:25:47,830 --> 00:25:49,700
Hit her! Hit her hard!

504
00:25:50,070 --> 00:25:51,220
What are you doing?

505
00:25:51,240 --> 00:25:52,180
Stop!

506
00:25:52,440 --> 00:25:53,610
Or I'll report it to the Patrol Office!

507
00:25:58,980 --> 00:25:59,960
