508
00:26:00,760 --> 00:26:01,420
Xia Yuan,

509
00:26:02,310 --> 00:26:03,130
pause for a second.

510
00:26:04,870 --> 00:26:05,660
Just look at me.

511
00:26:07,550 --> 00:26:08,460
What happened?

512
00:26:08,830 --> 00:26:09,700
Your wife

513
00:26:10,550 --> 00:26:12,700
cornered me at the café
