515
00:26:15,720 --> 00:26:16,290
Well.

516
00:26:17,200 --> 00:26:18,050
Shufen's doing?

517
00:26:18,390 --> 00:26:19,180
Let's talk inside.

518
00:26:19,200 --> 00:26:20,130
No!

519
00:26:20,920 --> 00:26:21,700
I'm not going anywhere.

520
00:26:21,960 --> 00:26:22,740
Talk right here.

521
00:26:23,590 --> 00:26:25,290
I got beaten because of you.

522
00:26:25,830 --> 00:26:26,850
Deal with this!

523
00:26:28,000 --> 00:26:29,130
Of course, I will.

524
00:26:29,870 --> 00:26:31,610
First go to the hospital.

525
00:26:32,000 --> 00:26:32,940
The best one.

526
00:26:33,110 --> 00:26:33,810
I'll cover all expenses.

527
00:26:36,000 --> 00:26:37,570
But this isn't just about money.

528
00:26:38,480 --> 00:26:39,570
I got beaten up!

529
00:26:39,590 --> 00:26:40,460
Do you see?

530
00:26:40,830 --> 00:26:42,740
They hit me. I was bullied!

531
00:26:42,960 --> 00:26:43,810
I know that much.

532
00:26:45,040 --> 00:26:46,610
What do you want me to do?

533
00:26:48,350 --> 00:26:49,130
Stop working.

534
00:26:49,440 --> 00:26:50,370
Drop what you're doing.

535
00:26:51,310 --> 00:26:52,130
Come with me to the hospital.

536
00:26:53,440 --> 00:26:55,130
But I have a very important meeting now.

537
00:26:55,150 --> 00:26:55,940
I can't go.

538
00:26:55,960 --> 00:26:57,090
I can't believe that!

539
00:26:57,110 --> 00:26:58,980
Look at me! I was bullied!

540
00:27:03,390 --> 00:27:04,900
Things have been overwhelming lately.

541
00:27:05,280 --> 00:27:06,770
Please stop causing trouble.

542
00:27:07,280 --> 00:27:08,530
