543
00:27:09,480 --> 00:27:10,610
Get your facts straight!

544
00:27:11,150 --> 00:27:12,460
Your wife is causing trouble.

545
00:27:15,110 --> 00:27:15,850
Alright.

546
00:27:16,200 --> 00:27:16,740
Here.

547
00:27:17,590 --> 00:27:19,130
