568
00:28:36,280 --> 00:28:38,020
You just took a wrong turn.

569
00:28:39,480 --> 00:28:41,660
It's not too late to turn back now.

570
00:28:43,550 --> 00:28:44,980
I planned

571
00:28:46,040 --> 00:28:47,460
to learn from him

572
00:28:48,720 --> 00:28:49,810
and use his money

573
00:28:50,590 --> 00:28:51,530
and his influence

574
00:28:52,550 --> 00:28:53,660
to start a business.

575
00:28:54,790 --> 00:28:56,570
But that was never going to work.

576
00:28:57,350 --> 00:28:57,900
I expected

577
00:28:58,720 --> 00:29:00,700
his wife can't stand me.

578
00:29:01,760 --> 00:29:02,530
But he

579
00:29:03,280 --> 00:29:04,850
never took me seriously.

580
00:29:06,760 --> 00:29:08,260
Since this way didn't work,

581
00:29:08,550 --> 00:29:10,130
try another one.

582
00:29:10,870 --> 00:29:12,050
What options do I have?

583
00:29:14,390 --> 00:29:15,660
I'm too old now.

584
00:29:16,590 --> 00:29:18,370
Nobody hires me for films anymore.

585
00:29:20,720 --> 00:29:21,810
Start a business?

586
00:29:22,830 --> 00:29:23,850
I don't have the capital for that.

587
00:29:25,440 --> 00:29:26,180
Get a job?

588
00:29:26,720 --> 00:29:27,770
But I can't handle hard labor.

589
00:29:28,070 --> 00:29:29,290
Marry someone?

590
00:29:29,630 --> 00:29:30,700
With my reputation,

591
00:29:30,720 --> 00:29:31,740
no man would ever want me.

592
00:29:32,310 --> 00:29:33,740
Work as a dancer at a nightclub?

593
00:29:35,830 --> 00:29:36,370
Erniu,

594
00:29:37,960 --> 00:29:39,740
why don't you join me instead?

595
00:29:42,790 --> 00:29:43,900
Join you?

596
00:29:46,200 --> 00:29:47,660
You helped Xia Yuan sell drugs,

597
00:29:48,110 --> 00:29:49,460
so you can help sell mine!

598
00:29:50,040 --> 00:29:51,330
Could I be useful to you?

599
00:29:52,790 --> 00:29:54,050
Join Shaohua Pharmaceuticals

600
00:29:54,830 --> 00:29:56,020
as the Vice General Manager

601
00:29:56,350 --> 00:29:57,220
focusing on sales.

602
00:29:58,150 --> 00:29:59,290
Beyond the salary,

603
00:29:59,760 --> 00:30:01,700
you'll receive 10% of shares.

604
00:30:03,150 --> 00:30:05,530
I don't have funds to buy back shares.

605
00:30:05,920 --> 00:30:07,700
You've paid far more than enough.

606
00:30:09,830 --> 00:30:10,850
Years ago,

607
00:30:11,390 --> 00:30:13,940
I needed capital desperately to launch

608
00:30:14,280 --> 00:30:15,460
Shaohua Pharmaceuticals.

609
00:30:16,350 --> 00:30:18,220
Just when I was at my wits' end,

610
00:30:19,200 --> 00:30:21,610
someone paid 80,000 silver dollars

611
00:30:22,000 --> 00:30:24,180
for my house
worth 40,000 silver dollars,

612
00:30:24,830 --> 00:30:26,420
saving me from disaster.

613
00:30:27,960 --> 00:30:28,770
That person turned out to be you.

614
00:30:29,680 --> 00:30:30,850
How did you find out?

615
00:30:32,070 --> 00:30:33,090
I've been wary

616
00:30:33,390 --> 00:30:35,980
of things that seem too good

617
00:30:36,000 --> 00:30:37,090
to be true,

618
00:30:37,830 --> 00:30:39,370
so I looked into it.

619
00:30:39,720 --> 00:30:41,980
Turns out it wasn't a gift from heaven

620
00:30:42,000 --> 00:30:43,130
nor a hidden snare.

621
00:30:43,150 --> 00:30:44,850
But your kindness toward me.

622
00:30:49,790 --> 00:30:51,500
All along, you knew.

623
00:30:52,920 --> 00:30:53,850
You never brought it up,

624
00:30:55,200 --> 00:30:57,220
so neither did I.

625
00:30:58,550 --> 00:30:59,220
But now,

626
00:31:00,200 --> 00:31:01,260
it's time for me

627
00:31:01,280 --> 00:31:02,810
to return your kindness.

628
00:31:04,480 --> 00:31:05,740
But

629
00:31:06,200 --> 00:31:07,420
it's far too much.

630
00:31:07,720 --> 00:31:08,610
Not at all!

631
00:31:09,720 --> 00:31:11,330
But for your help,

632
00:31:12,150 --> 00:31:13,980
Shaohua Pharmaceuticals wouldn't exist.

633
00:31:14,720 --> 00:31:17,260
Our dozen-year friendship

634
00:31:17,960 --> 00:31:19,610
can't be measured by money.

635
00:31:21,350 --> 00:31:22,290
Come work with me.

636
00:31:22,960 --> 00:31:23,770
Think of it as helping me out.

637
00:31:26,040 --> 00:31:27,050
But I worry

638
00:31:28,720 --> 00:31:31,020
I may let you down.

639
00:31:33,310 --> 00:31:34,290
Xia Yuan

640
00:31:34,310 --> 00:31:35,500
may be driven solely by profit,

641
00:31:35,520 --> 00:31:37,220
but he's an expert at closing deals.

642
00:31:37,760 --> 00:31:39,090
Having spent so much time with him,

643
00:31:39,310 --> 00:31:40,810
you must have picked up valuable skills.

644
00:31:41,760 --> 00:31:42,610
Next,

645
00:31:42,830 --> 00:31:43,980
I'll open branch factories

646
00:31:44,000 --> 00:31:45,020
and develop new drugs.

647
00:31:45,680 --> 00:31:46,420
I need you on this team.

648
00:31:47,680 --> 00:31:50,290
Xia Yuan might have corrupted me.

649
00:31:50,310 --> 00:31:51,090
Don't worry.

650
00:31:51,200 --> 00:31:51,700
Even if he has,

651
00:31:51,720 --> 00:31:53,570
I'm sure I can turn you around.

652
00:31:56,870 --> 00:31:57,420
OK!

653
00:31:58,200 --> 00:31:59,020
I'll work with you.

654
00:32:01,870 --> 00:32:02,530
Perfect!

655
00:32:04,200 --> 00:32:05,090
We can

656
00:32:05,760 --> 00:32:06,940
finally be together again!

657
00:32:10,390 --> 00:32:11,460
If ever

658
00:32:13,240 --> 00:32:14,740
I betray you,

659
00:32:15,590 --> 00:32:16,740
will you forgive me?

660
00:32:19,590 --> 00:32:20,740
We've weathered every storm

661
00:32:21,110 --> 00:32:22,660
side by side all these years,

662
00:32:24,480 --> 00:32:26,220
so nothing is unforgivable.

663
00:32:37,280 --> 00:32:39,500
Stamp as Mr. Xia said.

664
00:32:41,310 --> 00:32:42,260
Mr. Xu,

665
00:32:43,070 --> 00:32:44,460
don't you think this whole thing

666
00:32:46,480 --> 00:32:47,530
has taken an odd turn?

667
00:32:49,680 --> 00:32:51,770
Mr. Xia has his reasons.

668
00:32:51,790 --> 00:32:53,290
Don't worry.

669
00:32:55,590 --> 00:32:56,610
But it

670
00:32:57,870 --> 00:32:58,530
bothers me.

671
00:33:00,870 --> 00:33:02,500
Does taking the money bother you?

672
00:33:05,280 --> 00:33:06,330
Just stamp.

673
00:33:13,040 --> 00:33:13,810
Do you think

674
00:33:14,920 --> 00:33:18,330
he will let the Japanese join us?

675
00:33:19,630 --> 00:33:20,850
If they don't,

676
00:33:21,550 --> 00:33:22,900
we're all dead anyway.

677
00:33:22,920 --> 00:33:25,530
So be it! This is the worst time.

678
00:33:26,200 --> 00:33:28,050
We may start over from scratch.

679
00:33:29,310 --> 00:33:30,130
Easy for you to say.

680
00:33:30,280 --> 00:33:32,410
We're both nearly fifty.

681
00:33:32,560 --> 00:33:33,610
No second chances left.

682
00:33:33,760 --> 00:33:34,810
If push comes to shove,

683
00:33:35,520 --> 00:33:37,330
we could go back to farming.

684
00:33:37,630 --> 00:33:38,770
Even if you can,

685
00:33:39,070 --> 00:33:40,050
I can't.

686
00:33:40,920 --> 00:33:41,900
Enough, here!

687
00:33:42,390 --> 00:33:43,330
Hurry up and stamp.

688
00:33:51,310 --> 00:33:52,180
That's right.

689
00:33:52,240 --> 00:33:52,780
Hongnian.

690
00:33:53,720 --> 00:33:54,980
Gao, there you are!

691
00:33:56,000 --> 00:33:57,330
Mr. Xia wants you to prepare

692
00:33:58,800 --> 00:33:59,650
for next month's travel

693
00:34:00,560 --> 00:34:02,330
to north and northeast China.

694
00:34:03,870 --> 00:34:04,700
What's the mission?

695
00:34:05,040 --> 00:34:07,810
To revive our previously

696
00:34:08,070 --> 00:34:08,860
closed branches.

697
00:34:09,110 --> 00:34:10,780
Shouyuan Apothecary is saved?

698
00:34:11,750 --> 00:34:12,940
Good news indeed!

699
00:34:17,070 --> 00:34:17,940
It means

700
00:34:18,270 --> 00:34:18,690
we…

701
00:34:18,900 --> 00:34:20,700
Japanese investors
will own stakes in us.

702
00:34:29,440 --> 00:34:31,340
[Shanghai Shaohua Pharmaceuticals]
After making the rounds,

703
00:34:31,550 --> 00:34:33,420
I found several steps can be eliminated.

704
00:34:33,960 --> 00:34:36,170
That would cut production costs?

705
00:34:36,800 --> 00:34:37,530
By at least 30%.

706
00:34:37,840 --> 00:34:38,610
Wonderful!

707
00:34:40,360 --> 00:34:41,020
Ms. Chu,

708
00:34:41,590 --> 00:34:42,730
here's your letter that just arrived.

709
00:34:46,080 --> 00:34:47,420
I took detailed notes on everything.

710
00:34:47,590 --> 00:34:48,500
You can review them later.

711
00:34:50,580 --> 00:34:51,170
What's wrong?

712
00:35:04,360 --> 00:35:05,840
[Chu Shaohua, Get Out of Shanghai]

713
00:35:08,270 --> 00:35:09,500
It's an anonymous letter.

714
00:35:10,480 --> 00:35:11,050
Shaohua.

715
00:35:11,360 --> 00:35:11,980
Shaohua,

716
00:35:12,480 --> 00:35:13,380
Mr. Xia is waiting for you

717
00:35:13,630 --> 00:35:14,570
at Chichun Apothecary.

718
00:35:15,440 --> 00:35:16,340
Back then

719
00:35:16,960 --> 00:35:19,500
your mother and Zhou Yan transferred

720
00:35:20,440 --> 00:35:23,210
Chichun Apothecary signboard
and the Miracle Pill's formula

721
00:35:23,230 --> 00:35:24,290
to me to save Shaozhong.

722
00:35:24,630 --> 00:35:27,060
I'm sure you know this.

723
00:35:27,440 --> 00:35:28,130
That can't be right.

724
00:35:28,790 --> 00:35:29,860
In my memory,

725
00:35:30,480 --> 00:35:32,460
they only sold you

726
00:35:32,480 --> 00:35:33,250
Chichun Apothecary's signboard,

727
00:35:33,270 --> 00:35:34,290
not the Miracle Pill's formula.

728
00:35:35,110 --> 00:35:35,650
Yes.

729
00:35:37,000 --> 00:35:38,900
Back then, I only wanted the signboard.

730
00:35:39,920 --> 00:35:41,250
But your mother told me

731
00:35:41,750 --> 00:35:44,210
she'd also sell the formula

732
00:35:44,230 --> 00:35:46,130
for 50 silver dollars.

733
00:35:47,520 --> 00:35:48,940
Honestly, I didn't really want it.

734
00:35:49,440 --> 00:35:51,170
But she pleaded so earnestly

735
00:35:51,190 --> 00:35:52,090
and my heart softened.

736
00:35:52,560 --> 00:35:53,900
Ended up paying 50 silver dollars

737
00:35:54,230 --> 00:35:55,380
to take it off her hands.

738
00:35:59,400 --> 00:36:01,380
Gao and Yi Dajin were both present,

739
00:36:01,560 --> 00:36:02,460
so they can testify.

740
00:36:05,190 --> 00:36:07,020
I went with mother to meet Mr. Yi

741
00:36:07,040 --> 00:36:08,170
at Shouyuan Apothecary.

742
00:36:08,560 --> 00:36:09,250
We planned

743
00:36:10,150 --> 00:36:11,020
to drive up the price.

744
00:36:11,190 --> 00:36:12,210
Guess what?

745
00:36:12,520 --> 00:36:14,290
He seemed to know
we urgently needed cash

746
00:36:14,630 --> 00:36:16,650
and insisted on paying
only 128 silver dollars.

747
00:36:17,360 --> 00:36:19,460
Pity no one bought
the Miracle Pill's formula,

748
00:36:20,150 --> 00:36:21,610
or I could've scraped together cash
for you.

749
00:36:22,670 --> 00:36:24,290
If this whole thing were true,

750
00:36:25,270 --> 00:36:27,020
why would my mother and Zhou Yan

751
00:36:27,710 --> 00:36:30,130
have never mentioned it to me?

752
00:36:30,710 --> 00:36:31,650
And when Shaozhong

753
00:36:31,840 --> 00:36:34,690
gave me the Miracle Pill's formula,

754
00:36:35,270 --> 00:36:36,540
he never said a word about it.

755
00:36:38,080 --> 00:36:38,940
Not once?

756
00:36:38,960 --> 00:36:39,540
Yes.

757
00:36:43,190 --> 00:36:44,610
That's your family affair.

758
00:36:44,920 --> 00:36:45,900
I have no way of knowing.

759
00:36:46,880 --> 00:36:48,130
Perhaps

760
00:36:48,590 --> 00:36:50,090
they did tell you,

761
00:36:50,790 --> 00:36:51,730
yet

762
00:36:52,840 --> 00:36:53,500
you forgot.

763
00:36:56,080 --> 00:36:57,090
Or perhaps

764
00:36:59,040 --> 00:37:00,770
you spun some yarn

765
00:37:01,440 --> 00:37:02,860
about old days on a whim.

766
00:37:05,480 --> 00:37:08,380
Seems you refuse to buy into this.

767
00:37:10,270 --> 00:37:12,130
Why should I own up

768
00:37:12,670 --> 00:37:13,820
to baseless claims?

769
00:37:15,480 --> 00:37:16,170
No worries.

770
00:37:17,040 --> 00:37:17,860
All proof exists.

771
00:37:29,300 --> 00:37:30,960
[Contract]

772
00:37:38,630 --> 00:37:40,820
If this contract holds true,

773
00:37:41,190 --> 00:37:43,050
the Miracle Pill's formula

774
00:37:43,230 --> 00:37:45,170
must be in your hands now.

775
00:37:45,960 --> 00:37:47,170
Why did you

776
00:37:47,520 --> 00:37:48,540
come by today?

777
00:37:49,040 --> 00:37:49,610
Here's the thing.

778
00:37:50,750 --> 00:37:51,980
Back then Shaozhong held

779
00:37:52,080 --> 00:37:53,420
exclusive rights to that formula.

780
00:37:54,190 --> 00:37:55,500
When we drew up the contract,

781
00:37:55,640 --> 00:37:56,730
he was under arrest.

782
00:37:57,580 --> 00:37:59,090
Your mother took the money,

783
00:37:59,110 --> 00:38:01,050
but couldn't give the formula to me.

784
00:38:01,070 --> 00:38:02,860
Later when Shaozhong was released,

785
00:38:03,070 --> 00:38:05,650
I was too preoccupied

786
00:38:05,960 --> 00:38:07,170
as I mistakenly believed
Xia Chu's death.

787
00:38:08,380 --> 00:38:10,300
Then the business boomed

788
00:38:10,740 --> 00:38:11,920
and I just forgot about it.

789
00:38:12,670 --> 00:38:13,780
Recently,

790
00:38:14,480 --> 00:38:15,730
Gao fled here,

791
00:38:16,110 --> 00:38:18,020
bringing some documents

792
00:38:18,120 --> 00:38:18,940
from Shouyuan Apothecary.

793
00:38:19,270 --> 00:38:20,340
Only then did I remember this.

794
00:38:21,230 --> 00:38:22,130
So

795
00:38:22,670 --> 00:38:23,860
you came today

796
00:38:23,920 --> 00:38:25,380
seeking the formula.

797
00:38:26,110 --> 00:38:27,860
Though decades have passed,

798
00:38:28,070 --> 00:38:28,730
luckily, all documents

799
00:38:29,110 --> 00:38:29,980
remain intact.

800
00:38:30,840 --> 00:38:32,340
I hope you'll

801
00:38:32,880 --> 00:38:34,690
transfer the formula to me

802
00:38:35,110 --> 00:38:36,610
to honor the contract.

803
00:38:38,710 --> 00:38:41,300
Though the documents appear intact,

804
00:38:42,230 --> 00:38:44,460
I just don't buy it.

805
00:38:45,710 --> 00:38:48,130
You're denying your mother's thumbprint?

806
00:38:49,630 --> 00:38:51,050
She passed away years ago.

807
00:38:51,550 --> 00:38:53,020
There's simply no way

808
00:38:53,190 --> 00:38:54,650
to verify its authenticity.

809
00:38:55,270 --> 00:38:55,780
Fine!

810
00:38:57,190 --> 00:38:58,530
What about Zhou Yan's,

811
00:38:58,920 --> 00:39:00,500
Mr. Xia's, Gao's

812
00:39:00,620 --> 00:39:02,610
or even Anke Hall's Lei Yuting's?

813
00:39:02,800 --> 00:39:03,900
Can they be fake?

814
00:39:05,840 --> 00:39:08,460
It's easy to forge a fake certificate!

815
00:39:08,590 --> 00:39:09,460
You…

816
00:39:09,630 --> 00:39:10,170
Hongnian.

817
00:39:16,150 --> 00:39:16,860
Ms. Chu,

818
00:39:17,320 --> 00:39:18,940
I utterly understand your feelings.

819
00:39:19,320 --> 00:39:20,730
The success of the Miracle Pill

820
00:39:20,880 --> 00:39:22,420
stems from its miraculous formula,

821
00:39:23,630 --> 00:39:24,940
and your tireless efforts.

822
00:39:25,960 --> 00:39:26,940
How about this?

823
00:39:27,480 --> 00:39:29,780
I'm willing to cede

824
00:39:30,550 --> 00:39:32,650
half of its rights to you.

825
00:39:34,040 --> 00:39:34,610
Exactly 50%.

826
00:39:36,440 --> 00:39:38,210
That's my utmost sincerity shown.

827
00:39:39,270 --> 00:39:41,570
I also hope to see yours reflected.

828
00:39:42,270 --> 00:39:43,250
Mine

829
00:39:44,670 --> 00:39:45,900
means one thing.

830
00:39:46,230 --> 00:39:47,780
The Miracle Pill belongs
to the Chu family.

831
00:39:49,320 --> 00:39:50,860
It has nothing to do with you.

832
00:39:56,270 --> 00:39:57,730
If that's your stance,

833
00:40:00,230 --> 00:40:01,900
we'll settle this in court.

834
00:40:03,400 --> 00:40:04,460
Suit yourself.

835
00:40:08,670 --> 00:40:09,300
Fine.

836
00:40:16,440 --> 00:40:17,780
Once this hits court,

837
00:40:18,590 --> 00:40:19,570
your claim

838
00:40:21,230 --> 00:40:22,020
gets wiped clean to zero.

839
00:40:30,750 --> 00:40:32,780
Best cash out while you're ahead.

840
00:40:33,550 --> 00:40:36,170
Or you'll end up with nothing.

841
00:40:50,520 --> 00:40:52,130
The Miracle Pill

842
00:40:52,150 --> 00:40:53,090
is striking gold,

843
00:40:53,320 --> 00:40:54,780
so he wants a slice of profits.

844
00:40:55,880 --> 00:40:57,980
What he's after isn't a slice,

845
00:40:58,670 --> 00:40:59,900
but half the pie.

846
00:41:00,520 --> 00:41:02,420
Is that document genuine?

847
00:41:02,920 --> 00:41:04,210
I can't tell yet.

848
00:41:04,590 --> 00:41:06,090
Since even you can't tell,

849
00:41:06,520 --> 00:41:08,050
we'll flatly declare it fake,

850
00:41:08,070 --> 00:41:08,690
leaving him no choice.

851
00:41:12,070 --> 00:41:14,050
Yi Dajin is missing now,

852
00:41:14,360 --> 00:41:16,500
but the thumbprints
of Xia Yuan and Gao Qianyi

853
00:41:16,520 --> 00:41:17,530
seem authentic.

854
00:41:18,360 --> 00:41:19,860
I'm afraid the court rulings

855
00:41:20,150 --> 00:41:21,380
might favor them.

856
00:41:27,520 --> 00:41:28,940
What date does it say
for the court session?

857
00:41:29,630 --> 00:41:30,380
On the 15th day from now.

858
00:41:38,320 --> 00:41:38,860
Erniu,

859
00:41:39,670 --> 00:41:40,460
lend me a hand?

860
00:41:40,840 --> 00:41:42,050
Go find Zhou Yan.

861
00:41:42,670 --> 00:41:44,690
Even if she refuses to testify,

862
00:41:45,110 --> 00:41:46,460
just get her thumbprint.

863
00:41:46,480 --> 00:41:47,170
No problem.

864
00:41:47,960 --> 00:41:48,610
Cheng Hui,

865
00:41:49,040 --> 00:41:50,340
book me a ticket

866
00:41:50,360 --> 00:41:51,650
to Peking tomorrow.

